---
import '../styles/components/feature-grid.css';
---

<div class="features-grid">
  <div class="feat">
    <div class="feat-k">核</div>
    <div class="feat-label">Hardware</div>
    <h3>GPU-accelerated <em>hardburn</em></h3>
    <p>
      Uses your NVIDIA NVENC, Intel QSV, or AMD AMF to burn subs at 6–12× real-time. Your CPU stays
      free for other things.
    </p>
    <span class="feat-tag"><span class="ok">●</span> NVENC · QSV · AMF · VAAPI</span>
  </div>

  <div class="feat">
    <div class="feat-k">設</div>
    <div class="feat-label">Presets</div>
    <h3>Three knobs. <em>Zero</em> knob-turning.</h3>
    <p>
      Fast · Balanced · Pristine. The preset picks the encoder preset, CQ, and tune. Power users
      can edit the ffmpeg command directly.
    </p>
    <span class="feat-tag">速 · 均 · 極 · three ways to burn</span>
  </div>

  <div class="feat">
    <div class="feat-k">列</div>
    <div class="feat-label">Queue</div>
    <h3>Drop a cour. <em>Walk away.</em></h3>
    <p>
      Drag a whole folder in, MoeKoder pairs MKVs with their matching ASS files and chews through
      them one by one. Sleeps the machine when done.
    </p>
    <span class="feat-tag">12 episodes → one dinner</span>
  </div>

  <div class="feat">
    <div class="feat-k">録</div>
    <div class="feat-label">Transparency</div>
    <h3>Full ffmpeg <em>stderr.</em></h3>
    <p>
      No black boxes. Every frame, every warning, every bitrate line is right there in the side
      panel. Copy the command, paste it into a script, we don't mind.
    </p>
    <span class="feat-tag">ffmpeg 7.0.1 · unmodified</span>
  </div>

  <div class="feat">
    <div class="feat-k">夜</div>
    <div class="feat-label">Quiet</div>
    <h3>No cloud. <em>No account.</em></h3>
    <p>
      No sign-in, no update nag, no ping home. Launches into a quiet dark window and does one job
      well. Your files never leave your disk.
    </p>
    <span class="feat-tag"><span class="ok">●</span> 0 outbound connections</span>
  </div>

  <div class="feat">
    <div class="feat-k">無</div>
    <div class="feat-label">Free</div>
    <h3>Free. <em>Open.</em> Forever.</h3>
    <p>
      Source-available. Fork it, re-skin it, ship it (per LICENSE). No pro tier, no "upgrade to
      unlock", no paid codecs. Pay with a star on GitHub if you feel like it.
    </p>
    <span class="feat-tag">source available · github.com/Shironex/moekoder</span>
  </div>
</div>
